1. How NASA talks to satellites way the hell out there
High-level: it’s just radio, but done obscenely carefully.
1.1 The path
Command generated
On Earth, operators build a tiny packet of bits:
“rotate 0.01°”
“fire thruster for 2.3 seconds”
